summary: AN ORDINANCE authorizing execution and acceptance of a permit from Burlington Northern, Inc. to excavate for, construct, maintain and operate a 12-inch sanitary sewer pipe line; a 54-inch storm sewer pipe line; and a 36-inch storm sewer pipe line with one manhole, within said corporation's railroad right of way adjacent to West Lawton Way in the vicinity of 15th Ave. W. and W. Boston St., in Seattle, King County, Washington.
